        "content_1": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "About This Product",
            "heading": "UAE's Favourite STEM Drawing Robot for Kids",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p>The Kids STEM Drawing Robot is a <strong>screen-free creative toy</strong> that teaches children to draw step by step — automatically. Insert one of <strong>100+ template cards</strong>, press the button, and watch the robot draw outlines for your child to trace and colour.</p><p>No Wi-Fi. No apps. No subscriptions. Just hands-on creative play that builds <strong>fine motor skills, focus, and artistic confidence</strong> in children aged 4 to 10.</p><p><strong>Designed for UAE families.</strong> Whether your child is drawing animals after school in Dubai, practising shapes at home in Abu Dhabi, or staying entertained at a family gathering in Sharjah — this robot turns any moment into creative time. Compact enough for travel and silent enough for restaurants.</p><p>The <strong>4–5 hour USB rechargeable battery</strong> means no disposable batteries and no mid-session shutdowns. One charge covers a full week of daily 30-minute drawing sessions.</p><p><strong>Safe and certified.</strong> Non-toxic, BPA-free materials with smooth rounded edges. Includes washable markers that come off skin, clothes, and most surfaces easily.</p><p>TipTop360 delivers <strong>free next day across all 7 UAE emirates</strong> — Dubai, Abu Dhabi, Sharjah, Ajman, Fujairah, Ras Al Khaimah, and Umm Al Quwain. Cash on Delivery available. 14-day hassle-free returns.</p>",
            "alt_bg": true
          }
        },
        "content_2": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Everything Included",
            "heading": "What's in the Box",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<ul><li><strong>1x STEM Drawing Robot</strong> (Blue or Pink)</li><li><strong>100+ Drawing Template Cards</strong> — animals, shapes, objects, progressive difficulty</li><li><strong>12x Washable Colour Markers</strong> — non-toxic, washes off skin and clothes</li><li><strong>1x USB Charging Cable</strong></li><li><strong>1x Quick Start Guide</strong></li></ul><p><em>Works with standard A4 paper (not included). No batteries required — USB rechargeable.</em></p>",
            "alt_bg": false
          }
        },
