        "content_3": {
          "type": "content_section",
          "settings": {
            "label": "Built to Last",
            "heading": "Durability Kids Can't Break",
            "subheading": "",
            "body": "<p><strong>Premium ABS plastic</strong> with smooth rounded edges — designed to survive daily use by energetic children. No sharp corners, no small parts, no pinch points.</p><p>The <strong>USB rechargeable battery</strong> eliminates the cost and waste of disposable batteries. One charge delivers 4–5 hours of drawing time — enough for a full week of daily 30-minute sessions.</p><p><strong>Washable markers included</strong> — the 12 non-toxic colour markers wipe clean from skin, clothes, tables, and most surfaces. No permanent stains, no stress for parents.</p><p>The drawing mechanism is <strong>precision-engineered</strong> for smooth, consistent lines every time. Template cards are laminated for repeated use — they don't bend, tear, or wear out with regular handling.</p>",
            "alt_bg": true
          }
        }
